task.summary: Updated the whole system to use Hydra, instead of Cascade. Lots of changes have been done. Some performance improvements and some little enhancements.
A few more changes and improvements. Waiting for Hydra to implement session listener
Working. But the master is not balancing between the threads properly.
Improved some things. Works fine now. Some TODOs left. Next thing is going to be the description for the database.

Changed the master architecture so every MasterBotWorkerThread has its own MasterBotListener. This takes up more space, but makes it easier and less complicated to handle conflicts. Conflicts that would keep the listener from sending packets.
